  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In France, consumption of hypnotic drugs is high. In this context, and given the planned
      regulatory modifications, it seems essential to make an inventory of the consumption of drugs
      taken for a hypnotic purpose. This study aims to identify the substances (medical or not)
      used for a hypnotic purpose in the adult population going to a pharmacy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
